title: Slow Cooker Chunky Chicken Chili
directions: Combine beans, salsa, tomato sauce and chili powder in Slow Cooker. Top with chicken, onions and corn. (Do not stir.) Cover with lid.
Cook on LOW 6 to 8 hours (or on HIGH 4 to 5 hours); stir.
ingredients: 1 can (15.5 oz.) dark red kidney beans, rinsed
1 can (15.5 oz.) light red kidney beans, rinsed
1 can (15 oz.) no-salt-added tomato sauce or paste
1-1/2 lb. boneless skinless chicken thighs, cut into bite-size pieces
